IngressVLANStatus

Ingress VLAN lifecycle status.

enum IngressVLANStatus {
  CREATING
  ACTIVE
  FAILED
  REMOVING
}

Values

IngressVLANStatus.CREATING

VLAN is being created

IngressVLANStatus.ACTIVE

VLAN is active and ready

IngressVLANStatus.FAILED

VLAN creation/operation failed

IngressVLANStatus.REMOVING

VLAN is being removed

IngressVLAN object
